Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now see further than we've ever imagined,
