Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call... THE UNIVERSE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今和我们的幸存相关 神秘兮兮的 我们最近的邻居\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our closest neighbor, mysterious as it is, tied to our very survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自有人类开始它那亮度就一直迷惑着我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Its luminance has captivated us since the beginning of humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近一看揭示出一个永存的神话 争议和谜团之源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but a closer look reveals an ever-present source of myth, controversy and mystery.
