Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻觉与奇景的源头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a source of illusion and wonder,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个如此靠近人类之家的天体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a celestial body so close to home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有可能影响到我们的行为方式和我们的身体功能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it may impact the way we behave and the way our body functions.
