Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离地球约24万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Almost 240,000 miles from Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夜空中 我们的月球亮度胜过其它的天体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our Moon outshines every other celestial body in the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮… 当它升起带来光明时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Moon, when it's up and when it's bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我们产生梦想和惊叹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}makes us dream and wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们神秘的近邻也带来了无数\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our enigmatic neighbor is also the source of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悬而未决的谜团和历史悠久的神话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}countless unsolved mysteries and age-old myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球是个怪异的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Moon is a spooky place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从人类的角度来看这是个神秘的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a mysterious place from the human perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球看上去美丽而平淡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Moon is a beautiful and a really obvious thing to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们难以忽略这个天空中明亮的大球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's hard to miss, the big shining Moon in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我想所有的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, I think all people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在努力了解它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from all times have had some need to understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力适应它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some need to relate to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学会就宇宙的问题投射一束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Science may cast an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察之光在某些物体上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}empirical light on some things about the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而月球专家在提起月球时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But lunar experts are the first to admit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先会承认他们没有解决所有的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they don't have all the answers when it comes to our Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学是个过程\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Science is about process,
