Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而是这样吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1969年7月20日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}July 20th, 1969.
