Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈出了他历史性的一小步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}during that first visit to the lunar surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个人的一小步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's one small step for man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却是人类一个巨大的跨越\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one giant leap for mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在月球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}While on the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姆斯特朗报告了看到的东西 他称有个区域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Armstrong reported seeing what he called an area
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要比周围的区域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that is considerably more illuminated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明亮得多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than the surrounding area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个区域好象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that the area seems to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点点荧光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have a slight amount of fluorescence to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那表示什么意思呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近40年后的今天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today, almost 40 years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人确切地知道那光源究竟是什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no one knows exactly what that light source was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是科学家曾经目睹过类似的情形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But scientists have witnessed similar occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球上的整个等级的变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There been a whole class of changes on the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经涉及到明亮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that have involved brightenings,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜色的变化 甚至气体排放\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}color changes, and even gaseous emissions.
