Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文学家邦妮·布拉蒂那些人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}astronomer Bonnie Buratti,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称之为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}perplexed by what they call
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"月球瞬变现象"(LTP)的疑惑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Lunar Transient Phenomena", or LTPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球瞬变现象存在着争议\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Lunar Transient Phenomena are controversial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家很持怀疑态度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists are very skeptical about them.
