Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而从中世纪开始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But ever since the Middle Ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球观察家已经报告看到了那些神秘之光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lunar observers have reported seeing these mysterious lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常被看到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're usually witnessed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处在月球阴暗模糊的区域里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the dark shadowy areas of the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里对照更加强烈\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where the contrast is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会随机持续几秒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They last anywhere from a few seconds
