Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是它们很难确认的原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's why they've been so hard to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定了那些谜一般的表现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Convinced that these ethereal displays
