Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不能确定究竟是什么造成的确\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but unsure as to what's causing them,
