Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深入研究几个可能的解释\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in on several possible explanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于月球瞬变现象 已经有一些理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There have been a number of theories that have surfaced
