Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们已经将月亮与人的心理联系在了一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}people have associated the Moon with human psychology.
