Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多人广泛地坚信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a widely held belief
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中包括临床医生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}among many people including clinicians
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在满月的时候\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that during a full Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急诊室候诊有变化 明显的变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there are changes, palpable changes in emergency room visits,
