Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生率方面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in birthrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个神话说的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There is a mythology about behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行为举止随着月相而变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which changes consistently with the phases of the Moon.
