Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即满月对地球的居住者有没有明显的的作用呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that a full Moon has a measurable effect on the Earth's occupants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们早就试图将月球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People have long tried to associate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及月球的引力作用与人和动物的行为联系起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Moon, and the gravitational effects of the Moon with behavior in people and animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实是 月球搅动着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fact: the Moon stirs up the oceans
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占我们星球七成面积的海洋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which make up 70 percent of our planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此如果我们的身体是由70%的水组成的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if the human body is made up of 70 percent water,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不会意味着月亮也同样在拉扯着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}wouldn't that mean the Moon has just as much pull
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人体呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on human beings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些医学界德高望重的成员\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some respected members of the medical community
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已有报告 在满月时人的行为方面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have reported changes in human behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及生理学上的变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and physiology during full Moons.
