Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为仔细观察者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and as careful observers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续假设某种关系联系着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}continue to posit some relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月相变化与\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}between changes in the lunar cycle
