Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在执法部门有些人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are some in law enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为犯罪率会上升\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who believe the crime rates increase
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在满月时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when the Moon is full.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是第一线的其他人可不这么认为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But others manning the front lines aren't so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 这种说法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, the way i see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我个人看来像是个神话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}personally, I see it as a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在满月开始变化之时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At the start of a full Moon shift, deputy Jose Castro,
