Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘲笑那月球与人扯上关系的说法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}scoffed at the idea that a lunar pull has any effect on people.
