Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下我们正在响应488\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now we're responding to a 488,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是刚刚发生的盗窃案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is a theft that had just occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫称是个男人 讲西班牙语\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The call indicates that
