Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下我们正在响应273.5的呼叫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now we're responding to a call of the 273.5,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个现在正在发生的家庭暴力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is a domestic violence now that is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一段时期以来第一例家庭暴力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the first domestic violence we've had in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只是刚巧发生在满月\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it just so happens there is a full Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们正在去某个名流的途中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right now we are en route to a certain celebrity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就住在我们的区域内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that lives within our area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向名流的家投掷瓶子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The call states that a neighbor at this...celebrity's residence is throwing bottles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在报案者的前院\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the informant's front yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,截止到一年中最繁忙的周二夜晚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By the end of his busiest Tuesday night of the year,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副主管卡斯特罗的怀疑正开始减退\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}deputy Castro's skepticism was beginning to wane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我来说给你听\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, I'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在开始转变的那一刻我还是不大相信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At the beginning of the shift, I wasn't a big believer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在我成了信徒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But I'm becoming a believer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有许多是联系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A lot of this is tied to the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到月球引起地球上潮汐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the Moon causes tides on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么有可能会引起人体内的潮汐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so maybe it causes tides within people,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是不可能发生的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but that just can't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮对我们的身体是不会有潮汐作用的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Moon does not have a tidal effect on our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胸部没有因为月亮在拉扯而大起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My chest doesn't get bigger because the Moon is pulling on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得·普雷斯曼医生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dr. Peter Pressman,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛杉矶的西德斯西奈医学中心的一名医生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a medical doctor at Cedars-Sinai Hospital in Los Angeles,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认自己的一些同行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}acknowledged that some of his peers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信月球影响到人的行为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}believe that the Moon influences human behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生们相信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Physicians who believe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球确实影响到我们的身体和行为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that...the Moon does affect our bodies and our behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得出的结论是建立在他们观察的基础上的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}come to that conclusion on the basis of their observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些观察结果可能会遭到歪曲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And those observations may be very skewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们可能是场合性的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They may be very situational
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能并不能说明什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they may not mean a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非有人作为研究对象了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}except that that's what somebody has observed.
